---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — AI Compare Hub"
  description="Learn how AI Compare Hub reviews AI tools. Hands-on testing, no paid reviews, updated quarterly. Find out our review methodology."
>
  <article class="article">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="excerpt">
      <p>AI Compare Hub is a blog dedicated to testing and reviewing AI tools so you don't have to waste time and money on the wrong ones.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>How We Review</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Hands-on testing — we use every tool for at least 2 weeks</li>
      <li>No paid reviews — if it's bad, we'll say so</li>
      <li>Updated quarterly as tools evolve</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>Some links are affiliate links. If you buy through them, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. We only recommend tools we've tested and believe in.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>📧 hello@aicomparehub.blog</p>

    <p>Ready to explore? Browse our <a href="/tools">AI tool reviews</a>, see <a href="/comparisons">side-by-side comparisons</a>, or check out this week's <a href="/deals">deals</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "AboutPage",
  "name": "About AI Compare Hub",
  "url": "https://aicomparehub.blog/about",
  "description": "Learn how AI Compare Hub reviews AI tools. Hands-on testing, no paid reviews.",
  "isPartOf": {
    "@type": "WebSite",
    "name": "AI Compare Hub",
    "url": "https://aicomparehub.blog/"
  },
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://aicomparehub.blog/"},
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "About", "item": "https://aicomparehub.blog/about"}
    ]
  }
}
</script>
